<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/109568-if-you-had-to-pick-any-one-of-your">If you had to pick any one of your characters to be your new best friend (besides your wife) for the rest of your life, who would would it be and what do you imagine would be your weekend &quot;Let&#39;s hang out, but I don&#39;t want to plan anything, so let&#39;s do the &#39;usual&#39;&quot; ritual?</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/author/show/38550.Brandon_Sanderson"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/authors/1394044556i/38550._UX100_CR0,15,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/author/show/38550.Brandon_Sanderson">Brandon Sanderson</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think I&apos;d dig hanging out with Sazed. The usual would be, &quot;tell me about a religion you&apos;ve studied.&quot;<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think I'd dig hanging out with Sazed. The usual would be, "tell me about a religion you've studied."<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
