<div class="quoteText">
      &ldquo;You see, that is the sad, sorry, terrible thing about sarcasm.<br /><br />It's really funny.&rdquo;
  <br>  &#8213;
  <span class="authorOrTitle">
    Brandon Sanderson,
  </span>
    <span id=quote_book_link_623976>
      <a class="authorOrTitle" href="/work/quotes/2591148">Alcatraz Versus the Evil Librarians</a>
    </span>
    


<script>
